lead_paragraph: Tyler Roberson scored 18 points, fifth-year transfers Andrew White and John Gillon had 17 and 13 points apiece as No. 19 Syracuse overpowered upstate New York foe Colgate 83-55 on Friday night in the season opener for both teams.

headline.print_headline: No. 19 Syracuse Overpowers Upstate New York Foe Colgate
